# CODEOWNERS for terraform-aws-security-group
#
# This module manages reusable AWS security groups and their ingress/egress
# rules. Security has equity in every file, so the default rule routes
# review to both cloud-leads and security.
#
# Per Module-Repo Plan v1.x §16 governance.

# Default: every change requires both teams to approve.
*                          @devotica-labs/cloud-leads @devotica-labs/security

# CI/CD pipelines have privileged OIDC role assumption — security is
# explicitly an owner so a config slip cannot bypass review.
/.github/                  @devotica-labs/cloud-leads @devotica-labs/security
/.github/workflows/        @devotica-labs/cloud-leads @devotica-labs/security
